articles.title: Who's in Keir Starmer's new cabinet? - BBC.com
articles.description: Prime Minister Keir Starmer appoints Labour MPs to cabinet positions  after landslide election victory.
articles.content:
The country's new Prime Minister Keir Starmer has appointed 22 Labour MPs and peers to key cabinet positions - including a record 11 women - after the party's landslide election victory.
